data.description: MOTIVATED SELLERS!!! Welcome home to this charming four bedroom two bathroom home. This inviting open floorplan has had many recent upgrades such as, a new roof, new exterior paint and new interior paint in many of the rooms, new LVP flooring in the basement, light fixtures and xeriscaped front yard. You'll love those summer nights out on the screened in back patio. There is ample RV parking on the side of the home as well. Don't miss out on this great opportunity! Sellers have an FHA loan that is assumable with a 3.625% rate.
